data.name: male
data.description: of or denoting the sex that produces small, typically motile gametes, especially spermatozoa, with which a female may be fertilized or inseminated to produce offspring.

data.name: female
data.description: of or denoting the sex that can bear offspring or produce eggs, distinguished biologically by the production of gametes (ova) that can be fertilized by male gametes.

data.name: gay
data.description: sexually or romantically attracted exclusively to people of one's own sex or gender (used especially of a man).
